title: The Green Temple
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Take-out
description: A beautiful, open-air garden cafe in the South Bay that's decorated in colorful Asian and Indian themes. Menu features healthy salads, sandwiches, entrees, Mexican specialties, and herbal teas; desserts available (just ask). Highlights include the hearty loafs, savoury gold potatoes, and organic dressings. Friendly service.
